Itu mereka.

95
00:07:39,459 --> 00:07:41,002
- Itu dia?
- Di taksi itu?

96
00:07:45,214 --> 00:07:46,048
Sialan.

97
00:07:46,132 --> 00:07:47,884
Masih belum beres?

98
00:07:48,426 --> 00:07:51,262
Kenapa kau gagal menahan orang
yang tertangkap di TKP?

99
00:07:51,345 --> 00:07:52,472
Katamu dia pelakunya.

100
