Ya.

122
00:09:16,138 --> 00:09:19,225
Aku punya informasi baru.

123
00:09:20,309 --> 00:09:23,854
Aku memeriksa alibi Choi Jae-hee
dan rumah sakit mengonfirmasi

124
00:09:23,938 --> 00:09:26,107
Hong Hye-joo benar.

125
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:29,193
Jadi, Jae-hee benar-benar tak ada
di rumah sakit?

126
00:09:29,986 --> 00:09:31,362
Ya.

127
00:09:31,445 --> 00:09:35,366
Ada yang aneh,

128
00:09:35,449 --> 00:09:39,912
jadi aku memeriksa CCTV
di sekitar kediaman mereka.

129
00:09:39,996 --> 00:09:41,247
Lalu ternyata,

130
00:09:41,330 --> 00:09:43,624
dia terekam di sana.

131
00:09:44,333 --> 00:09:48,879
Menurut berita, anggota grupnya
ada di rumah sakit malam itu.

132
00:09:50,298 --> 00:09:51,382
