mungkin itu benar.

234
00:17:48,358 --> 00:17:49,985
Apa maksudmu "mungkin benar"?

235
00:17:50,069 --> 00:17:52,571
Dia konyol. Namanya berarti kuman.

236
00:17:53,447 --> 00:17:55,741
Namanya Kuman, kenapa dia mengejek namamu?

237
00:17:55,824 --> 00:17:58,702
Dia yang aneh. Kepribadiannya pun aneh.

238
00:18:51,964 --> 00:18:53,549
Aku lapar.

239
00:18:53,632 --> 00:18:55,509
Sebentar.

240
00:19:36,175 --> 00:19:38,635
Astaga, apa aku tak kasatmata?

241
00:19:40,053 --> 00:19:43,473
Bukankah seharusnya kau mengobrol
dengan orang yang makan bersamamu?

